**Why do students find it challenging to adapt their CVs and cover letters for each job?**
- Find it hard to match the background (CV) to the job application.
- Many students find it challenging to match their CVs to a customized cover letter. 
- To write a cover letter requires strong writing skills and the ability to emphasize the most relevant experiences.
- Many students do not know where to start or how to write a CV.
- Formulate their own skills/qualities when it comes to work experience and their background.
- The student do not know what is relevant for the job application.
